.cm SCRIPT REFERENCE RO
.SUBT Purpose
The ROMAN control word causes page numbers to use lower-case roman
numerals.
.SUBT Format
×
×  .RO
×
.SUBT Usage
The .RO control word causes all page numbers produced hereafter in
headings or footings to be printed in lower-case
roman numerals.
.SUBT Defaults
This command word will not create a break and unless encountered will
not be in effect.
.SUBT Notes
.of 4
(1) The ROMAN control word is equivalent to ".PN
.sp 1
.of 4
(2) Roman page numbering is supported only up to page 3999,
i.e. "mmmcmxcix".  Beyond this value results are invalid.
.cm End of RO
